## Code injection

``` php
$x = new \Djot\DjotConverter();
echo $x->convert('# Hi');
```

``` rust
fn main() {
    println!("hi");
}
```

## Math

Inline $a^2 + b^2 = c^2$ and display:

$$
\int_0^\infty e^{-x^2} \, dx = \frac{\sqrt{\pi}}{2}
$$

